        "meta_description": "Howard Hughes died 45 years ago today. The wealthy American was a businessman, pilot and filmmaker who went from dating beautiful movie stars to hiding away in hotel rooms, crippled by drug addiction and obsessive compulsive disorder",
        "meta_lang": "en",
        "meta_favicon": "https://s2-prod.dailystar.co.uk/@trinitymirrordigital/chameleon-branding/publications/dailystar/img/favicon.23503f7410f84687.ico",
